summary: Mythra Gallery was founded by professional group of artists and art patrons in 2015 as an alternative in the art category. Its name comes from Persian mythology( the god of light ). In Mythra Art gallery we present several generations of artists working; you will find international professional art works of different art styles and periods in our exhibitions. We believe it necessary to return aesthetics and reflection to daily life, and foster an ongoing dialogue with creativity, creations, and creators in general. We hope that our space will be a friendly meeting place for both artists and people interested in art.
